snippet.title: Algebra - Solve a compound inequality
snippet.description: This video shows how to solve a compound inequality.  Remember all the usual rules apply.  Also, what ever we do to one part, we must do to the other parts as well.  For more videos visit http://www.mysecretmathtutor.com
